Association of healthy lifestyle score with all-cause mortality and life 
expectancy: a city-wide prospective cohort study of cancer survivors.

Sun C(#)(1), Li K(#)(2), Xu H(#)(2), Wang X(1), Qin P(2), Wang S(2), Liang B(3), 
Xu L(4)(5).

Author information:
(1)School of Public Health, Sun Yat-sen University, Guangzhou, 510080, China.
(2)Chronic Noncommunicable Disease Prevention and Control Department, Guangzhou 
