Interaction between early in ovo stimulation of the gut microbiota and chicken 
host - splenic changes in gene expression and methylation.

Dunislawska A(1), Slawinska A(2), Gryzinska M(3), Siwek M(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Animal Biotechnology and Genetics, UTP University of Science 
and Technology, 85-084, Bydgoszcz, Poland. aleksandra.dunislawska@utp.edu.pl.
